flowchart TD
    A((A)) --> List[Search / filter residents<br/>by name · sitio · sector<br/>sortable table, PII masked]
    List --> Act{Action?}

    Act -- View detail --> Detail[Open read-only profile<br/>reveal masked PII]
    Act -- Export --> Exp[Export PDF / Excel]
    Act -- Import --> Imp[Upload CSV / XLSX] --> Parse[Parse & upsert rows] --> Save
    Act -- "Add / Edit (canEdit only)" --> Form[Fill sanitized form]

    Form --> Head{Marked as<br/>Household Head?}
    Head -- Yes --> NewHH[Auto-create household<br/>HH-0001 next number]
    Head -- No --> Link[Use selected household<br/>or none]
    NewHH --> Save[Save resident to Supabase]
    Link --> Save
    Save --> Audit[(audit_logs trigger)]
    Save --> Refresh[Refresh table]

    Detail --> R((R))
    Exp --> R
    Refresh --> R
